# Research Analyst — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your API keys.

# Required: Tavily API key for web search and content extraction.
# Get a key at https://app.tavily.com
TAVILY_API_KEY=your-tavily-api-key-here

# Required: OpenRouter API key for LLM access.
# Get a key at https://openrouter.ai
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-openrouter-api-key-here

# Optional: Reddit API credentials for discussion search.
# Create an app at https://www.reddit.com/prefs/apps
# REDDIT_CLIENT_ID=your-reddit-client-id-here
# REDDIT_CLIENT_SECRET=your-reddit-client-secret-here

# Optional: GitHub token to raise GitHub Search API rate limits.
# Unauthenticated GitHub search is limited to ~10 requests/min and degrades
# gracefully; a token raises the limit so the GitHub source runs reliably.
# Create a classic token (no scopes needed for public search) at
# https://github.com/settings/tokens
# GITHUB_TOKEN=your-github-token-here